  <title>Where does VirtualPC store disk images?</title>

  <p>By default, <app>VirtualPC</app> stores disk images in the folder
  <file>~/.local/share/lingmo-virtualpc/images/</file>. If you are using other
  software that interfaces with libvirt, such as <app>virt-manager</app>, then
  <app>VirtualPC</app> will also read from the folder that software uses to store
  its images.</p>

